SIMPLE: unincumbered
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unincumbered
<hw>Un`in*cum"bered</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Not incumbered; not burdened.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Law)</fld> <def>Free from any temporary estate or
interest, or from mortgage, or other charge or debt; <as>as, an estate
<ex>unincumbered</ex> with dower</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Uninfringible</ent>⟦br⟧
